{"id":345338,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":9}],"page":"3","source":"“不败的花”","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"225","ytitle":"","mtitle":"诗四首","ftitle":"","authors":["陈毅"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年来是与非，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生系得几安危。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩歌归去天与海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸦噪夕阳任鼓吹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断头今日意若何，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创业艰难百战多；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此去象台集旧部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旌旗十万斩阎罗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国烽烟二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此头须向国门悬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后死诸君多努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报飞来当纸钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廿年革命即为家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血雨腥风夜有人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取义成仁今日事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间种遍自由花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军文艺编者注:这四首诗，是陈毅元帅在皖南事变后，接到党中央革命军事委员会命令，任命他代理新四军军长以后，向全国人民表示斗争决心写成的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(原载解放军文艺四月号“不败的花”)"}]}